name: The ignorant wise
description: The ignorant wise man came to dinner with me in the delirium of the night, he did not stop or stop talking, he is the age of the earth but his knowledge is limited to what his eyes see, he speaks everything and in one of his intertwined words I He said that he lives in all living beings. The wise man feeds on insecurities and even if you don't see him, he breathes on the back of your neck at this moment.
